Klerksdorp Cluster Trio Task Team in partnership with Klerksdorp Detectives arrested three suspects in connection with the murder of a police officer. The three suspects, aged 27, 30 and 35 were arrested on Tuesday, 6 February, at about 15:00 in Alexandria, Gauteng.Cops spokesman Lieutenant Colonel Adéle Myburgh these said the arrests emanates from the gruesome murder of a 23-year-old police Constable Armand Wagner in North West on Monday, 5 February. "A motorist noticed the body of a man next to the road in Roosheuwel, Klerksdorp at about 21:35. The police were contacted and went to the scene. The body of a 23-year-old Constable was discovered with multiple stab wound, said Myburgh. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjsvAb7kzzVk2N00x7H0bB74MKoYzQHyUUmATMFqwprhNRFoB6bgKUBh0ROcEK-tbogEtYZT21zwnVLrJV0-kDuEbdefDbDLODiHJdNo32k1y28UxQdYkM_UYETo2WzMBGJMbFLGu1SjJY-WrhX4jrcSFi4GuDxyVmNMgB1ib9oGkGw7G4Zno-jC2Teqjm1MYv5VnQs7hy4oBqEP3NNgBuv6CSCVQaSvcQfwP4S8Euw3TxOPwIUM2A8LmEci5W1_X8Cm3ApjkWOHo7oBRN3V07PT14zvI1gw\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzK9WN_O57_NtEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
